<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans d. J. von Giech zu Burgellern und Ulrich Motschidler</head><p>Der Rat kündigt die betroffenen Nürnberger für Montag nach Weihnachten zu Bamberg an und hofft, dass sie dort von den Adressaten wegen der beschlagnahmten Habe ausgerichtet werden.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_556" id="277r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_556_r1l1"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von gıch dem <expan>Jung<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l3">Elrn vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Motſchıdler </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_556_r1l4">Hanns von gıch vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Motſchıdl<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den Jr hab von eẅch noch vngekeret ıſt gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l6">da Jr eẅch gütlıch mıt Jn eynen wellet etc das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l9">Vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_556_line_1592205372907_3308">dıe es angeet </ab></add> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / dıe ſprechen wıe Jn das Jr als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd niht <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> geſchehen mug / daʒ wir niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l11"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır mıt den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l12">daʒ ſıe auf den montag nach dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Crıſttag ſchıerıſt / gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l13"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> oder ſchıken <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getrawen wır eẅch wol . Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l14">tut den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> da ein <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> <expan>auſʒrıchtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd macht ſıe vnklag = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_556_r1l15">haft / daʒ wır fürbas klag von Jn <expan>erlaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_556" id="277r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> von Gich, dem
                        <expan>jung<ex>en</ex></expan>, zu Elrn und <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Motschidler </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Hanns von Gich und <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Motschidl<ex>er</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, den ir hab von ewch noch ungekeret ist,
                        gen <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, da
                        ir ewch gütlich mit in eynen wellet etc., das haben wir
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        mit den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <add>die es angeet</add>,
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt. Die sprechen, wie in das ir
                        als <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und niht <expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> geschehen mug, daz wir niht
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir mit
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt, daz sie auf den <app><note><q type="date">montag nach dem
                            <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> cristtag schierist</q>28.12.1422</note></app> gen
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> oder schiken <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getrawen wir ewch wol, ir tut den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> da ein
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan>
<expan>auszrichtu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und macht sie unklaghaft, daz wir
                        fürbas klag von in <expan>erlass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
